stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: POST /api/requests

    pending --> approved: user approves
    pending --> rejected: user rejects
    pending --> expired_approved: timeout · default = approve
    pending --> expired_rejected: timeout · default = reject
    pending --> cancelled: caller cancels

    approved --> [*]
    rejected --> [*]
    expired_approved --> [*]
    expired_rejected --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]
